{"title":"校园邮箱申请","icon":"apply","shareable":true,"id":"guide/account/mail/apply","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"text","type":"note","text":["只有 2022 级及之后的同学们，可以自行申请邮箱账号。","对于 2021 级及之前的同学们，邮箱账号是学校默认分配的，其格式为 “姓全拼 + 名首字母缩写 + 三位数字序号”。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"小程序申请"},{"tag":"list","header":"通过小程序是最简便的方式","items":[{"text":"邮箱申请","icon":"apply","url":"email-apply"}]},{"tag":"title","text":"官方申请流程"},{"tag":"text","text":["1. 登录网上服务大厅"]},{"tag":"action","header":"校内访问","content":"http://my.nenu.edu.cn/"},{"tag":"action","header":"校外访问","content":"https://my-443.webvpn.nenu.edu.cn/"},{"tag":"text","text":["2. 进行如下选择"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail-apply1.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","text":["3. 找到“个人邮箱申请”入口。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail-apply2.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","text":["4. 点击开始办理"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail-apply3.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","text":["5. 输入手机号并选择自己喜欢的邮箱名称"]},{"tag":"text","type":"note","text":["如果首选邮箱名称都已经被申请，那么你需要选择数字后缀并设置自己喜欢的数字后缀。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail-apply-select.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","text":["6. 填好信息后选择提交，如果你选择的邮箱用户名没有被占用，会弹出成功提示"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail-apply-success.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","text":["7. 点击确定后，系统会给出用户名和初始密码。请登录邮箱并修改。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail-apply-result.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"登录邮箱","path":"guide/account/mail/intro"}]},{"tag":"text","type":"warning","text":["请妥善截图或记录初始密码，如果不小心退出或忘记初始密码，请在首页中点击“我的申请查看”","目前在手机页面下无法正确显示邮箱密码，请使用 PC 版网页查看。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/account/mail-apply-password.jpg","watermark":true}],"time":"2024 年 6 月 16 日 03:54:15"}